<TIMEX3 tid="t3" type="DATE" value="2011-11-07">7 November 2011</TIMEX3> Last updated at 21:40 GMT Help Michael Jackson 's former personal doctor has been found guilty of involuntary manslaughter by a jury in Los Angeles .
Dr Conrad Murray , 58 was charged with causing the pop star 's death , attributed to a fatal overdose of the sedative propofol , in <TIMEX3 tid="t8" type="DATE" value="2009-06">June 2009</TIMEX3> , but had denied any wrongdoing .
During the six - week trial , 49 witnesses and more than 300 pieces of evidence were presented .
